{"tid":450300,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【超級光環】記錄傘運青年戰強權 黃之鋒紀錄片申請角逐奧斯卡","createTime":"2017-10-28T05:15:25.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-30T03:53:22.000Z","uid":79563,"like":43,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"5a6e7d184f62775a06c91c6e8986e1e753034dc0","tid":450300,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-28T05:15:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20171028/large/1509163628_5155.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171028%2Flarge%2F1509163628_5155.jpg&h=cd0dc525&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n「香港是我出生、成長及深愛的地方」，黃之鋒在外國電影中如此形容他對香港的想法。國際影音串流平台Netlix早前為香港眾志秘書長黃之鋒拍攝紀錄片，影片以《黃之鋒：熱血青年vs.超級強權》（Joshua: Teenager vs. Superpower）為題在今年5月26日作網上串流放映。美國電影藝術與科學學會周五公佈，《黃之鋒》一片有申請參賽，將會與其餘169套電影競逐奧斯卡金像獎最佳紀錄片。"},{"pid":"511672173e63fe1e159cba2d92445582aa1a5add","tid":450300,"uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-28T05:15:36.000Z","msg":"《黃之鋒：熱血青年vs.超級強權》一片全長1小時19分鐘，講述黃之鋒集結香港年輕學生參與佔領運動，成為內地當局口中其中一名「最惡名昭彰的異見者」的故事。電影以訪談形式為主，亦有訪問香港眾志成員周庭、主席羅冠聰等。"},{"pid":"c375ecb5e5b7505e2b91b3c3125f567563a76b70","tid":450300,"uid":3454,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-28T05:17:44.000Z","msg":"回帶<br />\n<br />\n香港唔配有黃之峰<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/361902/page/2?ref=web\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/361902/page/2?ref=web</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n樓豬當時仲食左唔少左膠負皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f24f45d0dd5822a8706d3858f9c9ef845c870597","tid":450300,"uid":138233,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-28T05:19:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4634dabc3f9aab381091f974af6e1695ddecabd","tid":450300,"uid":38539,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-28T06:38:44.000Z","msg":"之鋒好波"},{"pid":"1132588e65756629025b9fc85839ee