 noise, 對香港將來嘅可能性都係有好處。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n加泰事件話比我地知，如果國際社會唔撐你就點都無用</blockquote><br />\n連登仔話國際社會係廢<br />\nYou= 五毛"},{"pid":"0583298025d7c20f9f8f7f8b95af7af7d16c9ee7","tid":450300,"uid":49004,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-28T09:47:58.000Z","msg":"西方連加泰獨立都唔支持<br />\n虛偽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc6e25088274b34b43d501b40e575bb29497cb11","tid":450300,"uid":39277,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-28T10:31:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我理撚佢光唔光環。總之佢keep住係國際上make 到 noise, 對香港將來嘅可能性都係有好處。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n加泰事件話比我地知，如果國際社會唔撐你就點都無用</blockquote><br />\n其實你有強大的力量國際社會一定撐<br />\n<br />\n依家的俄國 北韓<br />\n國際社會都係尋求外交去解決<br />\n<br />\n以前中共推番國民黨<br />\n聯合國反而踢台灣走<br />\n<br />\n二戰未發生的納粹德國<br />\n英國初期咪又係默許佢地侵略行動<br />\n<br />\n如果加泰勢力勁過馬德里政府<br />\n最後國際社會咪又撐加泰<br />\n<br />\n根本邊個拳頭硬就邊個話事"},{"pid":"d8327174f17cd7a04962336865ae7112ee26d41e","tid":450300,"uid":39277,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-28T10:34:52.000Z","msg":"金仔擁核<br />\n<br />\n射多幾支飛彈落日本海<br />\n<br />\n美帝都吹佢唔脹<br />\n<br />\n其實要獨立就要核武<br />\n<br />\n台灣同加泰想獨立就要有核武"},{"pid":"07f39371b2fe617bed0553a7299e107c5d1e1461","tid":450300,"uid":47359,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-28T10:38:35.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">G phone</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><br />\n個人簽名 &times;按此隱藏<br />\n------------------------------------<br />\nOct 28近期活躍五毛<br />\n0群龍共舞 1天才小釣手 2三色貓 3JR 4法國佬巫斯義 <br />\n5吾系甘開心牙 6真律師何君堯 7蘇麗珊 8十卜ching <br />\n9D_wade 10RedBaron 11優美開始 12阿古路 13Romanov <br />\n14返六日唔撚易 15優美開始 16民國復興 17dewi <br />\n18侵b 19曼聯明叔 20bb chu 21小翁翁</span>"},{"pid":"2a0298bddbc0240b51e83f8768c0dda9ce6e76d2","tid":450300,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-28T10:39:50.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">雨傘的確啟蒙左唔少人<br />\n失敗左直情催生港獨</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1b5027c8ae6c2abf1887f61340729e38b967c80","tid":450300,"uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-28T10:51:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我理撚佢光唔光環。總之佢keep住係國際上make 到 noise, 對香港將來嘅可能性都係有好處。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nkeep住係國際上make 到 noise? make乜noise?<br />\n<br />\nkeep住同國際講反港獨？"},{"pid":"8df4ef70802b903fcdf4284673f30afe044848bf","tid":450300,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-28T10:51:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我理撚佢光唔光環。總之佢keep住係國際上make 到 noise, 對香港將來嘅可能性都係有好處。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n加泰事件話比我地知，如果國際社會唔撐你就點都無用</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n黃之鋒反港獨你知唔知?<br />\n<br />\nkeep住同國際講香港唔要獨立?"},{"pid":"e58a8c42f4a49c072bee14b83b3446e5f188a1c4","tid":450300,"uid":17008,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-28T11:22:45.000Z","msg":"外國勢力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22fd7cd95c63b929b6ad68988367b870c81985d1","tid":450300,"uid":3454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-29T04:23:07.000Z","msg":"民主自決<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">2047</span></span>"},{"pid":"7fed0e541c6c7f5f8575cb0b631221e4e3e406f1","tid":450300,"uid":47359,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-29T04:48:34.000Z","msg":"g phone其實堅勁<br />\n監禁g phone反而舉世敬重"},{"pid":"f2ec2e9e643180436dd53e8ee10e0e2beb09cd83","tid":450300,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-29T04:55:54.000Z","msg":"中共實干涉"}]}